extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Konami Digital Entertainment Inc, is proud to bring you our final booster product of 2024, Crossover Breakers that releases on December 6, 2024. Get ready to jump into the action with multiple new and unique themes in Crossover Breakers! This set contains multiple brand-new themes that introduce innovative strategies and will make for exciting Duels! Whether you are looking for something cool, cute, or a really big Dragon, Crossover Breakers has something for every kind of Duelist, and includes cards available as Collectors Rares and Quarter Century Secret Rares.
